# API Base URL Configuration
# 
# Dev on same machine (desktop):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000
#
# Testing from other device on LAN (mobile/tablet):
# Leave this variable blank/unset - the helper will automatically use http://<current-host>:3000
# Example: If accessing frontend at http://192.168.1.100:3001, API will use http://192.168.1.100:3000
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=
